---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<style>
  li {
    text-decoration: none;
    list-style-type: none;
  }
</style>

<BaseLayout
  pageTitle="About Us | XYZ Construction"
  description="Learn more about XYZ Construction and our mission to build excellence."
>
  <!-- About Section -->
  <section class="bg-gray-50 py-20 px-6 text-center">
    <div class="container mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">About XYZ Construction</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8 text-lg">
        Founded in 1987, XYZ Construction has been building dreams and
        shaping communities across the region for over three decades.
        What started as a small family-owned business with just three
        employees has grown into one of the area's most trusted
        construction firms, employing over 200 skilled professionals
        and completing more than 3,000 projects.
      </p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
        To deliver exceptional construction solutions that transform
        our clients' visions into reality while maintaining the
        highest standards of quality, safety, and environmental
        responsibility. We strive to build not just structures, but
        lasting relationships with our clients, employees, and
        communities.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">Who We Are</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
        At XYZ Construction, we pride ourselves on being more than
        just builders. We're problem solvers, innovators, and
        community partners. Our team brings together experienced
        project managers, skilled craftsmen, certified architects, and
        specialized engineers who work collaboratively to bring each
        project to successful completion.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">What We Do</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        Our comprehensive construction services span both residential
        and commercial sectors:
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">
        Residential Construction
      </h3>
      <ul class="text-gray-600 mb-6 list-disc pl-6">
        <li>Custom home building</li>
        <li>Major renovations and additions</li>
        <li>Kitchen and bathroom remodeling</li>
        <li>Basement finishing</li>
        <li>Outdoor living spaces</li>
        <li>Multi-family housing developments</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">
        Commercial Construction
      </h3>
      <ul class="text-gray-600 mb-8 list-disc pl-6">
        <li>Office buildings and corporate campuses</li>
        <li>Retail spaces and shopping centers</li>
        <li>Industrial facilities</li>
        <li>Healthcare facilities</li>
        <li>Educational institutions</li>
        <li>Restaurants and hospitality venues</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">Our Approach</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
        We believe in a client-centered approach that emphasizes open
        communication, transparency, and attention to detail. Every
        project begins with a thorough consultation to understand our
        clients' needs, budget, and timeline. Our experienced team
        then develops comprehensive plans that incorporate innovative
        solutions while adhering to the highest industry standards.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">
        Commitment to Excellence
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        Quality isn't just a buzzword at XYZ Construction â€“ it's
        embedded in everything we do. We maintain rigorous quality
        control processes and use only premium materials from trusted
        suppliers. Our commitment to excellence has earned us numerous
        industry certifications and awards, including:
      </p>
      <ul class="text-gray-600 mb-8 list-disc pl-6">
        <li>
          Associated Builders and Contractors Excellence in
          Construction Award (2022)
        </li>
        <li>Regional Contractor of the Year (2020, 2021)</li>
        <li>LEED Certification on over 50 projects</li>
        <li>A+ Rating from the Better Business Bureau since 1995</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">Sustainability</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        Environmental responsibility is a core value at XYZ
        Construction. We implement sustainable building practices
        whenever possible, including:
      </p>
      <ul class="text-gray-600 mb-8 list-disc pl-6">
        <li>Use of eco-friendly and recycled materials</li>
        <li>Energy-efficient design and construction methods</li>
        <li>Waste reduction and recycling programs</li>
        <li>Green building certification expertise</li>
        <li>Solar and alternative energy integration</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">
        Community Involvement
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        We believe in giving back to the communities we serve. Through
        our "Building Better Communities" initiative, we:
      </p>
      <ul class="text-gray-600 mb-8 list-disc pl-6">
        <li>
          Partner with local vocational schools to provide
          apprenticeship opportunities
        </li>
        <li>Donate construction services to local non-profits</li>
        <li>Sponsor community events and youth sports teams</li>
        <li>Participate in habitat restoration projects</li>
        <li>Provide disaster relief assistance</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">Safety First</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        Safety is paramount in everything we do. Our comprehensive
        safety program includes:
      </p>
      <ul class="text-gray-600 mb-8 list-disc pl-6">
        <li>Regular safety training for all employees</li>
        <li>Strict adherence to OSHA guidelines</li>
        <li>Daily safety inspections</li>
        <li>Zero-tolerance policy for safety violations</li>
        <li>EMR rating consistently below industry average</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">Looking Forward</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
        As we continue to grow, our commitment to excellence remains
        unchanged. We're constantly investing in new technologies,
        training our workforce, and expanding our capabilities to
        better serve our clients' evolving needs.
      </p>

      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
        Whether you're planning a small home renovation or a major
        commercial development, XYZ Construction has the expertise,
        resources, and dedication to bring your project to life.
        Contact us today to discover why so many clients trust us as
        their construction partner of choice.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="pt-4 flex items-center justify-center">
      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="bg-gradient-to-r from-slate-900 to bg-slate-700 text-white py-3 px-6 rounded-full text-lg hover:scale-95"
        >Contact Us</a
      >
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
